WEBVTT

00:00.088 --> 00:01.903
<i>Anyone who wins their</i>
<i>way past the threshold</i>

00:01.904 --> 00:04.179
<i>will behold the Book of Leaves.</i>
<i>Itself.</i>

00:04.180 --> 00:05.514
Now!

00:05.580 --> 00:07.849
Let's get
what we came here for.

00:07.917 --> 00:12.420
<i>I believe those symbols may imply</i>
<i>there are other ways out of here.</i>

00:12.488 --> 00:13.955
<i>You must kill the horse</i>

00:14.023 --> 00:15.957
<i>before it</i>
<i>snaps your neck.</i>

00:17.059 --> 00:18.927
<i>Ferrante.</i>
No more games!

00:18.995 --> 00:21.096
Have faith
that my plans proceed.

00:21.164 --> 00:23.198
I intend to take
my rightful place.

00:23.266 --> 00:25.433
The Sword of Osman.
It cannot be.

00:25.501 --> 00:26.935
And what is it
you want in return?

00:27.003 --> 00:28.503
To bring you to Rome.

00:28.571 --> 00:30.839
I am about to embark on a journey
to the den of my sworn enemy.

00:30.907 --> 00:32.473
Don't speak
to me of risk.

00:32.542 --> 00:34.176
This is not
what we agreed upon.

00:34.243 --> 00:36.444
You entered the vault
without me by your side.

00:36.512 --> 00:37.846
There's someone here.

00:40.283 --> 00:41.750
Leonardo!

00:41.817 --> 00:44.786
No! That's my mother!

00:44.854 --> 00:46.087
No!

